+/**
+ * SECTION:element-stridetransform
+ *
+ * stridetransform can be used to convert between video buffers
+ * with and without stride, or between buffers with differing
+ * stride
+ *
+ * <refsect2>
+ * <title>Example launch lines</title>
+ * |[
+ * gst-launch ???? TODO
